snippet.title: Kudamono Party - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Get ready for a fruit-fueled adventure! In this fast-paced puzzle game, launch and align fruits to rack up points and rise in the global ranks. With vivid graphics and engaging gameplay, it's a race against time to become the top fruit master. Dive in and challenge the world!

Developed by Kyberquest
NOTE: This is a clone of Suika Game, which was released on mobile.
